    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tiny Devils</strong>是一款快节奏的多人派对游戏，支持1-4名玩家。穿越疯狂的障碍赛道，利用蜜蜂和磁铁等强力道具干扰对手。抢到皇冠并冲向终点线—第一个到达的玩家获胜，但混乱是不可避免的！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>充满欢乐的混乱比赛</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202430/extras/a6400c1f82ffd68b93b2a7301fc169e8.poster.avif?t=1764074859\" width=698 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202430/extras/a6400c1f82ffd68b93b2a7301fc169e8.webm?t=1764074859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202430/extras/a6400c1f82ffd68b93b2a7301fc169e8.mp4?t=1764074859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>用创意道具击败对手：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>蜂刺</strong><br>释放一只蜜蜂，追赶对手，击中后让他们掉下皇冠。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202430/extras/98d80cf4a11b6e13881768923677e801.poster.avif?t=1764074859\" width=640 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202430/extras/98d80cf4a11b6e13881768923677e801.webm?t=1764074859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202430/extras/98d80cf4a11b6e13881768923677e801.mp4?t=1764074859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>磁力疯狂</strong><br>利用强大的磁力从对手那里夺取皇冠或附近的物品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202430/extras/33881a8e8606cde90edd196249682259.poster.avif?t=1764074859\" width=698 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202430/extras/33881a8e8606cde90edd196249682259.webm?t=1764074859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202430/extras/33881a8e8606cde90edd196249682259.mp4?t=1764074859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>陀螺翻转</strong><br>发射一个旋转的陀螺，它会在地图上反弹，击中对手后反转他们的控制。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202430/extras/55e8678538b05f58b6871550dcc44e50.poster.avif?t=1764074859\" width=698 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202430/extras/55e8678538b05f58b6871550dcc44e50.webm?t=1764074859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202430/extras/55e8678538b05f58b6871550dcc44e50.mp4?t=1764074859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>捣乱还是被捣乱</strong><br>在Tiny Devils中，一切皆有可能。把你的朋友从轨道上推开，偷走他们的道具，或者用烟雾弹阻挡他们的前进道路。但请小心—他们也可以这么对你。这是一场混乱的自由对战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>谁将戴上皇冠？</strong><br>只有最聪明、最快速、最狡猾的玩家才能获胜。你能战胜你的朋友，穿越混乱，获得胜利吗？加入Tiny Devils，看看你是否有资格戴上皇冠！</p>",
